1167.name: Dur 6 MoW
1167.Applications: Overlay welding on wear parts that need to outlast new parts where high temperatures combined with corrosion and wear resistance is required. 3D printing of parts for medical applications according class IIa medical device in accordance with annex IX rule 8 of the MDD 93/42/EEC. Composition corresponds to “type 4” CoCr dental material according to EN ISO 22674.
